Structure (1): A zoom lens for photographing including a first lens group having positive refracting power and a second lens group having negative refracting power both arranged in this order from an object, conducting variable power by changing a distance between the first lens group and the second lens group, and having a variable power ratio of 2.5 or greater and a field angle of not less than 70 (degree)  at a wide angle end, wherein the following conditions are satisfied;


1.25 <= Tw/Tt <= 1.8  (1)


0.60 <= fFc/fw <= 0.9  (2)
